desc_long								关于这款游戏							As a rookie musher, learn to foster a competitive and happy team of unique dogs so you can make your mark on the dogsledding capital of the nation!A well fed dog is a fast dog. Remember this, and your team will be unstoppable.Enter randomized races in one of seven increasingly challenging leaguesKeep your dogs fed during races to fend off fatigueWin races to earn moneyUse money to hire new dogsFind the best dogs for the job and give them practice to grow their skillLearn about the art of mushing from your mentor, and about your unique dogs by spending time with themImpress fans with flashy movesImpress sponsors with an army of fansDog Sled Saga has simple, pick-up-and-play racing, and deeper systems for dedicated players to uncover. Each unique dog's speed is hindered by hunger. Lob a limited supply of food to them to keep at full speed. Hazards on the track await.Additional FeaturesGamepad supportDynamic resolution						
